{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.880", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.360", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Regierung in Myanmar f\u00fchrt ethnische S\u00e4uberungen durch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.080", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Betroffen ist die muslimische Minderheit der Rohingya. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.920", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seit Jahren beobachtet die Bundesregierung diese Eskalation ohne konkrete Taten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.680", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung muss sich endlich daf\u00fcr einsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Armee die Gewalt gegen die Rohingya sofort beendet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle Rohingya m\u00fcssen an ihre Orte zur\u00fcckkehren k\u00f6nnen und die M\u00f6glichkeit haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.960", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Staatsb\u00fcrgerschaft zu erhalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Rechte dieser Menschen m\u00fcssen endlich wieder gesch\u00fctzt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeden Tag erleiden Rohingya Gewalt und Ausgrenzung durch die Regierung in Myanmar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am 25.\u00a0August 2017 ermordete das Milit\u00e4r mindestens 6\u00a0700\u00a0Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber 700\u00a0000\u00a0Rohingya fl\u00fcchteten seitdem aus dem Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Katastrophe ist die am schnellsten wachsende Fl\u00fcchtlingskatastrophe weltweit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.480", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist mittlerweile unumstritten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.320", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dies gezielte ethnische S\u00e4uberungen sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus diesem brutalen Versto\u00df gegen das V\u00f6lkerrecht durch die Regierung in Myanmar muss die Bundesregierung deutliche Konsequenzen ziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.640", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zeit dr\u00e4ngt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.280", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hunderttausende Rohingya sitzen in dem mittlerweile gr\u00f6\u00dften Fl\u00fcchtlingslager der Welt in Bangladesch fest. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeden Tag werden 16\u00a0Millionen Liter sauberes Trinkwasser ben\u00f6tigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.040", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Monatlich werden \u00fcber 12\u00a0000\u00a0Tonnen an Nahrungsmitteln gebraucht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.760", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dem im Juni anstehenden Monsun drohen noch mehr Leid und Zerst\u00f6rung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um die Katastrophe in Zaum zu halten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.440", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird der UNHCR in diesem Jahr 770\u00a0Millionen Euro ben\u00f6tigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern von der Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.800", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich mit einem erheblichen Anteil an dieser Summe zu beteiligen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.280", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nicht hinnehmbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.400", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Gruppe der \u00adRohingya in Myanmar zu staatenlosen Menschen erkl\u00e4rt wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.400", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie d\u00fcrfen nicht am politischen Leben teilnehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.640", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen nicht arbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.080", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kinder k\u00f6nnen nicht zur Schule gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben keine Rechte und sind der Willk\u00fcr des Staates ausgesetzt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um es klar zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder Mensch hat das Recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.160", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechte zu haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das steht in Artikel\u00a015 der Allgemeinen Erkl\u00e4rung der Menschenrechte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke fordert: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.800", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Staatenlosigkeit muss weltweit bek\u00e4mpft werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt global zwischen 10\u00a0Millionen und 15\u00a0Millionen staatenlose Menschen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.120", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kurdinnen und Kurden in Syrien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen mit russischen Wurzeln in Lettland und Estland und Sinti und Roma in ganz Europa. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Obwohl die Bundesregierung die Staatenlosen\u00fcbereinkommen unterzeichnet hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.080", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gibt es auch in Deutschland \u00fcber 21\u00a0000 staatenlose Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit vernachl\u00e4ssigt die Bundesregierung ihre internationalen Verpflichtungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht hinnehmbar."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Staatenlose Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.240", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in Deutschland leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.600", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brauchen Rechte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.240", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern ein Gesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um ihnen diese Rechte zu geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.160", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einb\u00fcrgerungen m\u00fcssen erleichtert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.760", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kinder von Gefl\u00fcchteten m\u00fcssen Geburtsurkunden erhalten k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.160", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Staatenlosigkeit bedeutet Ausgrenzung und Diskriminierung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.400", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Linke stimmte bereits im Mai\u00a02015 f\u00fcr den Antrag \u201eVerfolgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.880", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vertrieben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vergessen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.920", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "V\u00f6lkermord an den Rohingya verhindern\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gro\u00dfe Koalition lehnte den Antrag damals ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist unfassbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.920", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Situation muss anscheinend immer erst v\u00f6llig aus dem Ruder laufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bevor die Gro\u00dfe Koalition dazu Stellung nimmt und reagiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung darf nicht l\u00e4nger erst dann reagieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.800", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es bereits zu sp\u00e4t ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ausgegrenzte Gruppen m\u00fcssen Werkzeuge erhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.760", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um f\u00fcr sich selbst einzustehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.200", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern deshalb von der Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.320", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich auf EU- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und internationaler Ebene f\u00fcr die Abschaffung von Staatenlosigkeit einzusetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.920", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Partnerschaft zwischen zivilgesellschaftlichen Organisationen und staatenlosen Menschen zu f\u00f6rdern und zu finanzieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "besonders auf sexualisierte Gewalt gegen staatenlose Frauen einzugehen und angemessene finanzielle Mittel f\u00fcr bessere Informationen zu staatenlosen Bev\u00f6lkerungsgruppen bereitzustellen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.200", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jeder Mensch muss das Recht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.120", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rechte zu haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.800", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt erteile ich das Wort der Kollegin Margarete \u00adBause, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen."
   ]
  }
 ]
}